<%
  @title = "Document Contributors"
%>

<h1>Document Contributors</h1>

<p>The organizations below have agreed to work with us during our development phase. Definitely check out the <a href="/featured">reporting</a> they've already done with DocumentCloud.</p> 
		
<p>If you have original documents and you're interested in using DocumentCloud -- it's free -- <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>

<h2>Initial Partners</h2>

<ul>
  <% @partners.each do |name, url| %>
    <li><a href="<%= h(url) %>"><%= h(name) %></a></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<h2>Contributing Organizations</h2>

<ul>
  <% @contributors.each do |name, url, title| %>
    <%= p(name.inspect) %>
    <li><a href="<%= h(url) %>"<%=if title then " title=\"#{h(title)}\"" end %>><%= h(name) %></a></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

